%^BOLD%^Priests %^RESET%^are able to select at least one domain from those offered by your deity. Multiclass priests will be able to select one domain, and singleclass priests will be able to select two. This can be done at churches and temples using <pick domain x>, where x is the domain you wish to have access to.

%^GREEN%^Rangers %^RESET%^will find themselves able to access spells from the %^GREEN%^animal %^RESET%^and %^GREEN%^plant %^RESET%^domains.

%^YELLOW%^Paladins%^RESET%^ and %^BOLD%^%^BLACK%^antipaladins %^RESET%^will find themselves able to access spells from the %^BOLD%^vigilance %^RESET%^and %^BOLD%^protection %^RESET%^domains.

%^BOLD%^Be aware %^RESET%^- you cannot change your mind on a domain you choose later on, so choose wisely. Domains available to each god can be seen in the specific helpfiles for each deity, eg/ <help tymora>, and in <help deities>.

%^BOLD%^Domain spells are as follows:
------------------------------------------------------------------
Air          whispering wind, airbolt, windstorm
%^CYAN%^Animal       ghost step, snakebite, rage
Cavern       meld into stone, maw of stone, earthquake
%^CYAN%^Charm        good hope, bliss, charm monster
Cold         ice shield, frost breath, hypothermia
%^CYAN%^Creation     minor creation, glyph of warding, cometfall
Darkness     armor of darkness, darkbolt, listening shadow
%^CYAN%^Destruction  shatter, tremor, disintegrate
Earth        strength of stone, earth reaver, stone body
%^CYAN%^Evil         blight, unholy orb, blasphemy
Fate         auspicious bolt, aegis of fate, fortune fate
%^CYAN%^Fire         fire shield, handfire, flameburst
Good         bless, holy orb, holy word
%^CYAN%^Illusion     displacement, screen, weird
Knowledge    comprehend languages, wieldskill, forgotten melody
%^CYAN%^Magic        true seeing, mystic bolt, break curse
Mentalism    insight, bolt of force, inner eye
%^CYAN%^Moon         faerie fire, moonbeam, silver sight
Plant        entangle, meld into nature, thorn spray
%^CYAN%^Protection   divine shield, invisibility purge, teleportation ward
Renewal      rejuvenation, freedom of movement, rebirth
%^CYAN%^Repose       phantom steed, spectral touch, ghostform
Storms       lightning touch, stormwinds, stormrage
%^CYAN%^Strength     righteous might, resilience, crushing hand
Sun          nimbus of light, searing light, sunburst
%^CYAN%^Travel       faithful mount, pass portal, create portal
Trickery     conceal alignment, befuddle, confusion
%^CYAN%^Tyranny      oppression, fear, forbiddance
Vigilance    orders oath, mark of justice, weighed in the balance
%^CYAN%^War          seeking sword, offensive summoning, berserker
Water        cloudburst, mist of the goddess, tidal surge

See also: cleric, deities, individual help files for each deity,
          and individual help files for each domain
